 * Helper to check if array S is a cyclic rotation of array B.
 * Assumes B and S have the same length k.
 * If k=0, returns true (vacuously).
 * If k>0, it checks rotation property.
 * @param {number[]} B 
 * @param {number[]} S 
 * @param {number} k 
